## Commands

```bash
# Install dependencies
uv sync

# Run notebook (edit mode)
uv run marimo edit notebooks/example.py

# Run notebook (read-only)
uv run marimo run notebooks/example.py

# Create new notebook
uv run marimo edit notebooks/new_notebook.py

# Linting
uv run ruff check .
uv run ruff format .

# Type checking
uv run pyrefly check
```

